KABOKWENI &#8211; An alleged car thief was admitted to hospital last night after he was shot during a car chase.Two suspects reportedly stole a Nissan 1400 in Clau Clau yesterday.With the assistance of Bossies Community Justice&#8217;s Albert Gryvenstein, KaBokweni&#8217;s police were able to track down the vehicle.According to Gryvenstein, two suspects sped off with the bakkie when police approached it. A car chase ensued and shots were fired. &#8220;One suspect escaped and the other was injured. He was transported to hospital where he is recovering from gunshot wounds,&#8221; said Gryvenstein.&nbsp;